addition of \f(CW\*(C`agg\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`concat\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`drop_cols\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`rank\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`rename_cols\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`select_cols\*(C'\fR functions
