.Vb 5
\& # This is a comment
\& id,name,val
\& 1,Alice,10.5
\& 2,Bob,
\& 3,Charlie,15.2
.Ve
.PP
would not be read correctly using \f(CW\*(C`read_table\*(C'\fR, but now is read correctly
